flowchart TB

Start([START])
Welcome[/PRINT Welcome/]
ReadID[/PRINT Enter ID\nREAD idNumber/]
VerifyID{VERIFY_ID OK?}
VerifyFail[/PRINT Verification failed/]
End([END])
Verified[/PRINT Identity verified/]

Menu[/PRINT Select action\n1 Appointment\n2 Test Results\n3 Exit\nREAD action/]
ExitQ{action is 3?}
Goodbye[/PRINT Goodbye/]

ApptQ{action is 1?}
TestQ{action is 2?}
InvalidSel[/PRINT Invalid selection/]

AgainAsk[/PRINT Another action YES or NO\nREAD again/]
AgainQ{again is YES?}

%% Appointment module
ApptTitle[/PRINT Appointment Module/]
ReadClinic[/PRINT Select clinic\nREAD clinic/]
GetDoctors[doctorList = GET_DOCTORS]
ReadDoctor[/PRINT Select doctor or BACK\nREAD doctor/]
DoctorBackQ{doctor is BACK?}
GetSlots[timeSlots = GET_AVAILABLE_SLOTS]
SlotsEmptyQ{timeSlots empty?}
NoSlots[/PRINT No slots choose another doctor/]

ReadSlot[/PRINT Select slot or BACK\nREAD slot/]
SlotBackQ{slot is BACK?}
SlotAvailQ{slot available?}
SlotNotAvail[/PRINT Slot not available/]

ConfirmAsk[/PRINT Confirm YES or NO\nREAD confirm/]
ConfirmQ{confirm is YES?}
CreateAppt[CREATE_APPOINTMENT]
ApptConfirmed[/PRINT Appointment confirmed/]
SendSMS[SEND_SMS]
SMSSent[/PRINT SMS sent/]
NotConfirmed[/PRINT Appointment not confirmed/]

%% Test results module
TestTitle[/PRINT Test Results Module/]
TestsExistQ{tests exist?}
NoTests[/PRINT No tests found/]
ReadyQ{results ready?}
NotReady[/PRINT Results not ready yet/]
GetResults[results = GET_RESULTS]
DisplayResults[/DISPLAY results/]
DownloadAsk[/PRINT Download PDF YES or NO\nREAD download/]
DownloadQ{download is YES?}
GenPDF[GENERATE_PDF]
PDFMsg[/PRINT PDF downloaded/]

%% Flow
Start --> Welcome --> ReadID --> VerifyID
VerifyID -- No --> VerifyFail --> End
VerifyID -- Yes --> Verified --> Menu

Menu --> ExitQ
ExitQ -- Yes --> Goodbye --> End
ExitQ -- No --> ApptQ

ApptQ -- Yes --> ApptTitle --> ReadClinic --> GetDoctors --> ReadDoctor --> DoctorBackQ
DoctorBackQ -- Yes --> AgainAsk
DoctorBackQ -- No --> GetSlots --> SlotsEmptyQ
SlotsEmptyQ -- Yes --> NoSlots --> ReadDoctor
SlotsEmptyQ -- No --> ReadSlot --> SlotBackQ
SlotBackQ -- Yes --> ReadDoctor
SlotBackQ -- No --> SlotAvailQ
SlotAvailQ -- No --> SlotNotAvail --> ReadSlot
SlotAvailQ -- Yes --> ConfirmAsk --> ConfirmQ
ConfirmQ -- Yes --> CreateAppt --> ApptConfirmed --> SendSMS --> SMSSent --> AgainAsk
ConfirmQ -- No --> NotConfirmed --> AgainAsk

ApptQ -- No --> TestQ
TestQ -- No --> InvalidSel --> AgainAsk

TestQ -- Yes --> TestTitle --> TestsExistQ
TestsExistQ -- No --> NoTests --> AgainAsk
TestsExistQ -- Yes --> ReadyQ
ReadyQ -- No --> NotReady --> AgainAsk
ReadyQ -- Yes --> GetResults --> DisplayResults --> DownloadAsk --> DownloadQ
DownloadQ -- Yes --> GenPDF --> PDFMsg --> AgainAsk
DownloadQ -- No --> AgainAsk

AgainAsk --> AgainQ
AgainQ -- Yes --> Menu
AgainQ -- No --> End
